üîê AuthController
POST   http://localhost:8580/auth/signup       # Create new user
POST   http://localhost:8580/auth/login        # Authenticate user
POST   http://localhost:8580/auth/refresh      # Refresh JWT token

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
üë§ UserController
PUT    http://localhost:8580/user/update       # Update user info
GET    http://localhost:8580/user/profile      # Fetch user profile

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
üìù NoteController
POST   http://localhost:8580/notes/create      # Create a new note
PUT    http://localhost:8580/notes/update      # Update note content/title
DELETE http://localhost:8580/notes/delete      # Delete note
POST   http://localhost:8580/notes/share       # Share note with other users
PUT    http://localhost:8580/notes/notify      # Set notification for note
POST   http://localhost:8580/notes/comments    # Add comment to a note

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
üë• GroupController
POST   http://localhost:8580/groups/create     # Create new group
POST   http://localhost:8580/groups/join       # Add user to group
DELETE http://localhost:8580/groups/remove     # Remove user from group
GET    http://localhost:8580/groups/list       # List groups user belongs to

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
üîî NotificationController
POST   http://localhost:8580/notifications/create   # Create notification
PUT    http://localhost:8580/notifications/update   # Update notification status
GET    http://localhost:8580/notifications/list     # List user notifications
